name: Splatoon Characters
description:
NEWEST: ACTUALLY COMPETENT TAGGING. ALL EXAMPLE IMAGES ON COMBINED V2 ARE RAW GENS


THESE ARE LORAS FOR THE MAIN SIX SPLATOON CHARACTERS: CALLIE, MARIE, PEARL, MARINA, SHIVER, AND FRYE.

THESE ARE NOT LORAS FOR GENERATING INKLINGS OR OCTOLINGS IN GENERAL. MODELS LIKE AOM3 CAN ALREADY DO THAT JUST FINE.

NEW: Combined LoRA. this is the recommended version to use unless you know what you're doing.

If you're having problems getting a certain character to generate properly(this is most noticeable with shiver), try not including a species tag.

Trained on NAI

(Also keeping up the individual LoRAs. Wouldn't recommend using them, but hey, I'm not your dad)


\/-------------------- OLD DESCRIPTION --------------------\/

6 LoRAs, 6 characters.

Pearl, Marina, Callie, Marie, Shiver, Frye

Marina and Shiver are trained on AOM2-sfw
The rest are trained on NAI

All attached LoRAs are epoch 6, and all example images were made with 0.8 LoRA weight
